{"id":103182,"type":2,"name":"ヤンキー烈風隊","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9e/b8/103182_SRQCy.jpg","summary":"月刊少年マガジン（講談社刊）誌上にて約7年間という長期連載となった、もとはしまさしげの暴走族漫画をOVA化した作品。ケンカでは負けなしの主人公・門田紋乃丞。とあることから巨大暴走族「ブラック・ツェッペリン」八代目総長の花岡竜二に目をつけられた紋乃丞だったが、彼の身代わりとして、レディース「すみれ一家」のミチがブラック・ツェッペリンに襲われてしまう。怒る紋乃丞は竜二にヤキを入れるが、竜二は広域暴力団「関東花岡連合会」会長・花岡虎造の息子で……。息子への仕打ちのケジメをつけろと、花岡邸へ呼び出しを食らった紋乃丞の行動とは……!?","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>6</li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/1951\">青山充</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Yankee Gale Squad</li><li><span>发售日: </span>1989/03/17</li><li><span>导演: </span>今沢哲男</li><li><span>原作: </span>もとはしまさひで</li><li><span>脚本: </span>小野竜之助丶 石倉保志丶 中西隆三</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":398470,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398470","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":398471,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398471","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":398472,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398472","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":398473,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398473","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":398474,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398474","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":398475,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/398475","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":1951,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d9/78/1951_prsn_5H5UW.jpg","name":"青山充","desc":"原画"}]}